===獎項===
2010年，《摩登家庭》問鼎五個[[電視評論家協會獎|電視評論家協會獎]]（Television Critics Association Award），獲得最佳新劇、最佳喜劇、年度最佳節目的提名，另外泰·布瑞爾、艾力克·斯通斯特里特、傑西·泰勒·佛格森、索菲婭·維嘉娜和朱莉·鮑溫都各自獲得演員獎項的提名。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tvguide.com/News/TCA-Award-Nominations-1019206.aspx|title=Modern Family Tops Nominations for TV Crtics Association Awards|publisher=TVGuide.com|access-date=2012-01-07|archive-date=2017-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171203013937/http://www.tvguide.com/news/tca-award-nominations-1019206/|dead-url=no}}</ref>為了強調《摩登家庭》的群戲演出，劇組就像《老友記》一樣在艾美獎只提交最佳喜劇類男/女配角，<ref>Melillo, Amanda (April 13, 2010) {{cite news |url=http://www.nypost.com/p/entertainment/tv/fam_united_stand_SbuCBeGiCcv9B8x7oxNRpL |title=? |author= |date=2010-04-13 |work= |publisher=[[New_York_Post|New York Post]] |accessdate=2010-06-24 |first=Amanda |last=Melillo |archive-date=2010-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100416165827/http://www.nypost.com/p/entertainment/tv/fam_united_stand_SbuCBeGiCcv9B8x7oxNRpL |dead-url=no }}</ref>最後此劇嬴走了最佳喜劇、喜劇類最佳編劇、喜劇類最佳男配角（艾力克·斯通斯特里特獲獎）。2011年時，此劇亦嬴得了[[美國演員工會獎|美國演員工會獎]]的喜劇類最佳整體效果，擊敗了上屆嬴家《[[歡樂合唱團|歡樂合唱團]]》。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sagawards.org/media-pr/press-releases/17th-annual-screen-actors-guild-awards-%C2%AE-nominations-announcement |title=17th Annual Screen Actors Guild Awards ® Nominations Announcement | Screen Actors Guild Awards |publisher=Sagawards.org |date= |accessdate=2010-12-16 |archive-date=2015-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150928212016/http://www.sagawards.org/media-pr/press-releases/17th-annual-screen-actors-guild-awards-%C2%AE-nominations-announcement |dead-url=yes }}</ref>另外，《摩登家庭》也獲得{{link-en|Gay, Lesbian and Straight Education Network|Gay, Lesbian and Straight Education Network|GLSEN}}的尊重獎，表揚此劇建立了「一個多元化美國的正面形象和故事線，包括描繪一個同性伴侶家庭」（"positive images and storylines that reflect a diverse America, including the depiction of a family headed by a gay couple"）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.abcmedianet.com/assets/pr/html/100710_20.html |title=GLSEN TO HONOR ABC’S MODERN FAMILY |author=Rou, Allison |date=2010-10-07 |work=ABCmedianet |accessdate=2010-10-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604124209/http://www.abcmedianet.com/assets/pr/html/100710_20.html |archivedate=2011-06-04 }}</ref>

2011年的[[第63屆黃金時段艾美獎|第63屆黃金時段艾美獎]]裡，《摩登家庭》以十七項提名排行第三最多提名的電視節目，排在《[[廣告狂人|廣告狂人]]》和《[[海濱帝國|海濱帝國]]》（''Boardwalk Empire''）之後。<ref name="emmy11">{{cite web |url=http://www.hitfix.com/articles/nominees-for-the-63rd-primetime-emmy-awards |title=Nominees for the 63rd Primetime Emmy Awards |author=HitFix Staff |date=2011-07-14 |work=[[HitFix|HitFix]] |accessdate=2011-07-14 |archive-date=2011-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716172942/http://www.hitfix.com/articles/nominees-for-the-63rd-primetime-emmy-awards |dead-url=no }}</ref>獲提名的獎項包括最佳喜劇、喜劇類最佳男/女配角、最佳喜劇類編劇、最佳喜劇類導演等，最後此劇嬴走五個獎項（布瑞爾嬴得男配角，而鮑溫嬴得女配角），成為當年艾美獎的最大嬴家。<ref name="emmy11"/>除了艾美獎之外，《摩登家庭》亦連續三年都獲[[金球獎_(影視獎項)|金球獎]]及[[金衛星獎|金衛星獎]]（Satellite Award）提名，雖未嬴得金衛星獎，不過《摩登家庭》已連續三年都獲得[[皮博迪獎|皮博迪獎]]年度十佳電視節目和於[[第69屆金球獎|2012年]]奪得金球獎音樂或喜劇類最佳劇集的殊榮。在2013年6月美国作家协公布的101部最有名的电视连续剧中排名''第''34位<ref>{{Cite web|title=‘101 Best Written TV Series Of All Time’ From WGA/TV Guide: Complete List|url=https://deadline.com/2013/06/wgas-101-best-written-tv-series-of-all-time-complete-list-512061/|accessdate=2020-04-08|date=2013-06-03|last=Team|first=The Deadline|work=Deadline|language=en|archive-date=2013-06-03|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6H5yn3sZq?url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/06/wgas-101-best-written-tv-series-of-all-time-complete-list/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年12月，又在《电视指南》评选的60个最佳系列榜单中排行第43位<ref>{{Cite web|title=TV Guide Magazine's 60 Best Series of All Time {{!}} TV Guide|url=https://www.tvguide.com/news/tv-guide-magazine-60-best-series-1074962/|accessdate=2020-04-08|date=2013-12-23|work=TVGuide.com|language=en|archive-date=2016-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161003105507/http://www.tvguide.com/news/tv-guide-magazine-60-best-series-1074962/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年[[第66屆黃金時段艾美獎|第66屆黃金時段艾美獎]]，再度獲得喜劇類最佳影集<ref>[http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201408260103-1.aspx 第66屆艾美獎主要得獎名單] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201408260103-1.aspx |date=20140826080218 }}，中央社，2014年8月26日</ref>。

除了獎項外，《摩登家庭》也經常登上評論家推介的電視節目排行榜上。2010年，BuddyTV推介它為2009-2010年十佳喜劇之一、2009年十佳節目的第二位，<ref>Kubicek, John {{Cite web |url=http://www.buddytv.com/slideshows/modern-family/the-best-comedies-of-the-tv-season-6773.aspx |title=? |author= |date= |work= |publisher=BuddyTV |accessdate=2010-06-24 |archive-date=2010-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100811104754/http://www.buddytv.com/slideshows/modern-family/the-best-comedies-of-the-tv-season-6773.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>而在《時代》亦排行2009年十佳節目的第二位。<ref>Poniewozik, James (December 8, 2009) {{cite news |url=http://tunedin.blogs.time.com/2009/12/08/top-10-shows-of-2009-the-best-and-the-rest/ |title=? |author= |date=2009-12-08 |work=Time |publisher= |accessdate=2010-06-22 |archive-date=2011-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110824031107/http://tunedin.blogs.time.com/2009/12/08/top-10-shows-of-2009-the-best-and-the-rest/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>《[[電視指南|電視指南]]》亦選擇《摩登家庭》為「大家最愛戴的家庭」（Our Favorite Families）之一。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tvguide.com/PhotoGallery/Favorite-TV-Families-1024402#1024422 |title=Our Favorite TV Families |author= |date= |work=[[TV_Guide|TV Guide]] |accessdate=2010-10-21 |archive-date=2014-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141019150506/http://www.tvguide.com/PhotoGallery/Favorite-TV-Families-1024402#1024422 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===收視率===
自這部劇集首播以來，《摩登家庭》一直獲得廣泛支持和收看。在它的首個季度裡，它成為全美18-49歲收視率<ref name="Nielsen">美國的收視率是由[[尼爾森媒體研究|尼爾森媒體研究]]（Nielsen Media Research）公司所計算。其中以18-49歲收視率對劇集的播映最為重要，甚至比觀眾人數更重要，因為這群觀眾的消費力較高。故此這群觀眾的收視率愈高，免費電視台的廣告收益就愈高，對該劇的延續和取消有很大影響力。</ref>中排名第六最高的節目，是新劇中排第三位的節目。<ref name="tvhit"/>在第一季結束後，此劇嬴得了艾美獎最佳喜劇，推高了第二季的收視，令它成為首播週星期三最高收視的電視節目，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/09/23/abc-turns-in-its-strongest-wednesday-in-nearly-10-months-modern-family-opens-as-wednesday%E2%80%99s-no-1-tv-show/64820 |title=ABC Turns in its Strongest Wednesday in Nearly 10 Months; ‘Modern Family’ Opens as Wednesday’s No. 1 TV Show |author=Seidman, Robert |date=2010-09-23 |work=TVbythenumbers |accessdate=2010-09-23 |archive-date=2010-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100926115841/http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/09/23/abc-turns-in-its-strongest-wednesday-in-nearly-10-months-modern-family-opens-as-wednesday%E2%80%99s-no-1-tv-show/64820 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>比上一季在18-49歲收視率上升了34%。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/10/21/glee-dancing-modern-family-castle-lead-seasons-ratings-gainers-csiny-lie-to-me-house-lead-losers/69042 |title=Glee, Dancing, Modern Family, Castle Lead Season’s Ratings Gainers, CSI:NY, Lie To Me, House Lead Losers |author=Gorman, Bill |date=2010-10-21 |work=TVbythenumbers |accessdate=2010-10-21 |archive-date=2010-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101024182830/http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/10/21/glee-dancing-modern-family-castle-lead-seasons-ratings-gainers-csiny-lie-to-me-house-lead-losers/69042 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>《摩登家庭》經常登上18-49歲觀眾中最高收視節目的排行榜之中。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/11/02/tv-ratings-broadcast-top-25-nfl-modern-family-glee-ncis-dwts-top-week-6-viewing/70478 |title=TV Ratings Broadcast Top 25: NFL, Modern Family, Glee, NCIS, DWTS Top Week 6 Viewing |author=Seidman, Robert |date=2010-11-02 |work=TVbythenumbers |accessdate=2010-11-02 |archive-date=2010-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101104235840/http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/11/02/tv-ratings-broadcast-top-25-nfl-modern-family-glee-ncis-dwts-top-week-6-viewing/70478 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/10/26/tv-ratings-broadcast-top-25-brett-favre-modern-family-two-and-a-half-men-ncis-dwts-the-big-bang-theory-top-week-5-viewing/69680 |title=TV Ratings Broadcast Top 25: Brett Favre, Modern Family, Two and a Half Men, NCIS, DWTS, The Big Bang Theory Top Week 5 Viewing |author=Seidman, Robert |date=2010-10-26 |work=TVbythenumbers |accessdate=2010-10-26 |archive-date=2010-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101027194417/http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/10/26/tv-ratings-broadcast-top-25-brett-favre-modern-family-two-and-a-half-men-ncis-dwts-the-big-bang-theory-top-week-5-viewing/69680 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="top25">{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/10/19/tv-ratings-broadcast-top-25-modern-family-glee-greys-anatomy-glee-sunday-night-football-dwts-ncis-top-week-4-viewing/68590 |title=TV Ratings Broadcast Top 25: Modern Family, Glee, Grey’s Anatomy, Glee, Sunday Night Football, DWTS, NCIS Top Week 4 Viewing |author=Seidman, Robert |date=2010-10-19 |work=TVbythenumbers |accessdate=2010-10-19 |archive-date=2010-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101022045851/http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/10/19/tv-ratings-broadcast-top-25-modern-family-glee-greys-anatomy-glee-sunday-night-football-dwts-ncis-top-week-4-viewing/68590 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>此劇的成功足與經典喜劇《考斯比一家》（''The Cosby Show''）媲美。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118026163.html?categoryid=14&cs=1 |title='Modern Family' is a 'Cosby' celebre |author=Weisman, Jon |date=2010-10-21 |work=''[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]'' |accessdate=2010-10-24 }}</ref>在2010至2011年的美國電視節目季度裡，《摩登家庭》是18-49歲觀眾收視率中排行最高的劇集，而在全國人口計算的收視率中則於情景喜劇類中排名第三，僅次於CBS的兩部當紅情景喜劇，《[[生活大爆炸|生活大爆炸]]》和《[[好漢兩個半|好漢兩個半]]》。<ref name="seasontworating">{{cite web |last=Gorman |first=Bill |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/06/01/2010-11-season-broadcast-primetime-show-18-49-ratings-averages/94402/comment-page-2/#comments |title=2010-11 Season Broadcast Primetime Show 18-49 Ratings Averages - Ratings | TVbytheNumbers |publisher=Tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com |date=2011-05-26 |accessdate=2011-06-02 |archive-date=2014-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028125140/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/06/01/2010-11-season-broadcast-primetime-show-18-49-ratings-averages/94402/comment-page-2/#comments |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="seasontwoviewer"/>此季亦是[[数字视频录像机|數位視訊錄影機]]觀眾人數之中最高的節目。<ref>{{cite web |last=Gorman |first=Bill |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/06/13/modern-family-tops-dvr-ratings-gain-for-the-2010-11-season-fringe-has-biggest-increase-by-dvr/95418/ |title=‘Modern Family’ Tops DVR Ratings Gain For The 2010-11 Season; ‘Fringe’ Has Biggest % Increase By DVR - Ratings | TVbytheNumbers |publisher=[[TV_by_the_Numbers|TV by the Numbers]] |date=2011-06-09 |accessdate=2011-06-13 |archive-date=2011-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110616110035/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/06/13/modern-family-tops-dvr-ratings-gain-for-the-2010-11-season-fringe-has-biggest-increase-by-dvr/95418/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>《摩登家庭》第三季的回歸繼續了一貫的強勢，成為ABC六年以來最高收視的復播集。<ref name="preliminaryratings">{{cite web |author=Seidman, Robert |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/09/22/tv-ratings-wednesday-x-factor-no-idol-modern-family-premieres-big-revenge-gets-nice-start-csi-svu/104503/ |title=TV Ratings Wednesday: ‘X Factor’ No ‘Idol’; ‘Modern Family’ Premieres Big; ‘Revenge’ Gets Nice Start; CSI > SVU - Ratings | TVbytheNumbers |publisher=[[TV_by_the_Numbers|TV by the Numbers]] |date=2011-09-22 |accessdate=2011-10-25 |archive-date=2011-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110924103650/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/09/22/tv-ratings-wednesday-x-factor-no-idol-modern-family-premieres-big-revenge-gets-nice-start-csi-svu/104503/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>《摩登家庭》的成功更令人開始覺得此劇是衰落中的[[情景喜劇|情景喜劇]]的救星，引領著情景喜劇的重生。<ref>{{cite web |last=Villarreal |first=Yvonne |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/la-ca-modern-family-20111030,0,3791963.story |title='Modern Family': Savior of the sitcom |publisher=''[[The_Los_Angeles_Times|The Los Angeles Times]]'' |date=2011-10-30 |accessdate=2011-10-29 |archive-date=2011-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111030135453/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/la-ca-modern-family-20111030,0,3791963.story |dead-url=no }}</ref>

